Umphathi we-IK - Isu Elingumnyombo Wokuthuthukisa: Abaphathi be-IK kumele bazibandakanye ngokunomqondo ohlelweni kuwo wonke amazinga kanye nakakhulkazi kunqubo yokuthatha izinqumo.
