Ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuthi umyalo uhlala ukhona, lomthethonkambiso uthi kufanele ulokhu ubuyekezwe.
Ngaphansi kwaleMithethonkambiso uMqondisi-Jikelele kufanele abukeze umyalo wokuphoqwa okungenani njalo ezinyangeni ezintathu, bese kuthi njalo ngemuva kokubukezwa , aqinisekise, aguqule noma achithe isinqumo esibhaliwe.
